properties.areaDesc: Port Washington to North Point Light WI; Sheboygan to Port Washington WI; Wind Point WI to Winthrop Harbor IL; North Point Light to Wind Point WI
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 3 at 9:23AM CST until February 4 at 12:00PM CST by NWS Milwaukee/Sullivan WI
properties.description:
* WHAT...North northeast winds 15 to 20 kt with gusts up to 30
kt. Waves of 4 to 7 feet are expected from Sheboygan to Port
Washington. From North Point Light to Winthrop Harbor IL,
waves between 6 to 9 feet are expected.

* WHERE...Sheboygan to Port Washington to North Point Light to
Wind Point WI to Winthrop Harbor IL.

* WHEN...From 9 PM this evening to noon CST Tuesday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT FROM 9 PM THIS EVENING TO NOON CST TUESDAY
